snippet.title: Doki Doki Literature Club Plus! - Launch Trailer - Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
Okay, everyone! Doki Doki Literature Club is NOW AVAILABLE on the Nintendo Switch! Write poems for your crush and experience the terror of school romance in this critically-acclaimed psychological horror story! https://ddlc.plus/

Buy here: https://www.nintendo.com/games/detail/doki-doki-literature-club-plus-switch/  

#DDLC #NintendoSwitch

Subscribe for more Nintendo fun! https://goo.gl/HYYsot

Visit Nintendo.com for all the latest! http://www.nintendo.com/
